{"tid":1602384,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇Bio 5**既人可以分享下心得","createTime":"2019-09-29T11:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:38:08.000Z","uid":250073,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"70e085b1bf3cf7fa1cd3f9befff4d384705f6aa0","tid":1602384,"uid":250073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"小弟考左2次，都係得5，好想試下摘星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自問唔太識寫essay,睇到條題之後唔知解題。<br />\n同埋elective，㨂左E1 E2 ，目前pass paper嘅數量唔多，操得唔夠。<br />\n今年準備考第三次，幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0aca91fe6ff2f765562c62081eb44ce8833105","tid":1602384,"uid":61831,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:48:23.000Z","msg":"唔好揀E2, 轉攻E4"},{"pid":"341f8ec9a4baa8578a5432046f93a11dcde3460c","tid":1602384,"uid":61831,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"E2呢個單元<br />\n好處: 非BIO普通人都可以靠常識拎合格分數<br />\n壞處: 太多變化好難高分"},{"pid":"a3a34670c7596f881d3c5800e35be75637854125","tid":1602384,"uid":228436,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"有pass paper有無fail paper"},{"pid":"327f8d201472140be9df9d7402536d7ace0f7d82","tid":1602384,"uid":41155,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"食曬成本恐龍書佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老老豆豆呢科你背得曬就高分<br />\n<br />\n利申：5** E1 E2"},{"pid":"d2d08a671d1bc9eac2218dd67d579b6b15cd7e68","tid":1602384,"uid":120678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"唔清楚而家bio呢科同以前係咪仲係一樣玩法<br />\n但以前黎講基本上都係考記性<br />\n利申當年CE bio A，大學其中一個degree係Biochemistry"},{"pid":"d544b54fbffe607fcfe1c0749f1d396